</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_75" id="36r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm von Meyental, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, burgrafen <expan>Joh<ex>ansens</ex></expan>,
                        hofmeister </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her hofmeister, als ir uns <expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habt
                        von Otten Heydens, <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan></add>, und des Hansen Herolts von
                        Ültfeld wegen, darümb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, czurede gesaczt und der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Hans Herolt hinter im sicz und den mit
                        tür und tör besliesz und wöll auch den <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan>,
                        als reht sey; und nimt <add>der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>,
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>,</add> fremde, daz ir euch ümb
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Herolt annemt.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan>
<expan>Bap<ex>tista</ex>
<hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
